---
import { Picture } from "astro:assets";
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import PageHeader from "../components/PageHeader.astro";
import SocialIcons from "../components/SocialIcons.astro";
import wexlPhoto from "../assets/wexl.webp";

const title = "About";
const description =
  "Software engineer at Sigma Technology. Backend, embedded, automotive. Based in Budapest.";
---

<Base title={title} description={description}>
  <PageHeader eyebrow="About" title="A bit about " accented="me.">
    <Fragment slot="lede">
      Software engineer at <strong>Sigma Technology</strong> in Budapest. Six years on automotive software
      at Continental before this — mostly embedded and large-scale C. Outside work: forests and trails.
    </Fragment>
    <div class="about-social">
      <SocialIcons />
    </div>
  </PageHeader>

  <article class="prose">
    <h2>Stack</h2>
    <p>
      C, C++, Python, Vue, Docker. Comfortable in Linux, CI/CD, and anything that needs to run fast
      and not lie about it. Dabbling in Swift and SwiftUI for a side project when I have the
      patience for Xcode.
    </p>

    <h2>Currently</h2>
    <p>
      Going deeper on Python internals. Playing with LLM tooling — prompts, agents, the whole messy
      surface. Writing here when something's worth writing down.
    </p>

    <h2>Background</h2>
    <p>
      Grew up in Veszprém, Hungary. Started by taking apart broken computers; eventually got paid to
      do the software equivalent. Continental taught me how million-line codebases stay alive. Sigma
      is where I got autonomy back.
    </p>

    <h2>Beyond the terminal</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Mountain biking — mostly the Wexl Trails when I can get out there.</li>
      <li>Counter-Strike, when I want to forget about work for an hour.</li>
      <li>A homelab that exists mainly so I have something to break and fix.</li>
    </ul>

    <Picture
      src={wexlPhoto}
      alt="Wexl Trails, Austria"
      widths={[640, 880, 1280]}
      sizes="(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px"
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
      formats={["avif", "webp"]}
    />

    <h2>Colophon</h2>
    <p>
      Built with <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a> and plain CSS. Deployed via GitHub Actions to
      GitHub Pages.
      <a href="https://github.com/vakesz/vakesz">Source</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</Base>
